## From Foreground to Fading Background
[](https://medium.com/@katiebarnett5?source=post_page---byline--bea553dd97ff---------------------------------------)[Katie Barnett](https://medium.com/@katiebarnett5?source=post_page---byline--bea553dd97ff---------------------------------------)Follow6 min readÂ·Jan 8, 2024[
